---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "About SyntaxSnap | Built for Speed & Privacy";
const description = "SyntaxSnap provides local-first developer tools. No server uploads, no ads, just instant utilities for modern web development.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12 px-4">
    
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6">The "Local-First" Promise</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg text-slate-300 space-y-6">
      <p>
        Most developer tools are broken. You paste your sensitive JSON or private images into a random website, 
        wait for it to upload to a server you don't trust, and then download the result.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        <strong class="text-indigo-400 text-xl font-bold italic block my-4">SyntaxSnap is different.</strong>
      </p>
      
      <p>
        We believe in <strong>Local-First Development</strong>. When you use our tools, 
        your data <em>never leaves your browser</em>. The logic runs entirely on your device. 
        This isn't just a feature; it's our core architecture.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">The Cuddalore Connection</h2>
      <p>
        SyntaxSnap is an indie project maintained by the <strong>DigiTekLab</strong> team. 
        We are proud to build world-class software from <strong>Cuddalore, Tamil Nadu</strong>. 
      </p>
      <p>
        By focusing on efficiency and the latest web standards like <strong>Astro 5.0</strong> and <strong>React 19</strong>, 
        we prove that top-tier developer utilities can be built with transparency and local pride, far away from the traditional tech hubs.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 p-6 rounded-2xl my-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 mt-0">Why use SyntaxSnap?</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 marker:text-indigo-500">
          <li><strong>Zero Latency:</strong> No server round-trips. Instant results.</li>
          <li><strong>100% Privacy:</strong> Your API keys and client data stay on your machine.</li>
          <li><strong>No Fluff:</strong> No pop-up ads, no newsletter walls, no trackers.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 italic">
        Hosting on Cloudflare Edge. Built with ❤️ for the global dev community.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>